OL,7,FScampi is at risk of disappearing
OL,8,Ffrom pub menus because of new visa
OL,9,Frequirements for foreign fishermen,
OL,10,Fministers have been warned.
OL,12,FUnder changes to the visa system made
OL,13,Fin March, fishermen coming to work in
OL,14,Fthe UK will need to apply for a
OL,15,Fskilled migration visa, which
OL,16,Frequires a written English test.
OL,18,FThe Home Office has refused to give
OL,19,Fexemptions for the sector, despite
OL,20,Fwarnings of a longstanding worker
OL,21,Fshortage.
